Text:
@Delron

Don't play movies through your console, just go buy a $60-$80 WD TV Live off eBay and you'll never have to worry if the movie will play right on your PS3 again.  I have a WD TV Live and it has played back 99% of everything I've downloaded off here.

If you have no idea what a WD TV Live is, just go to Amazon and type it in and read all the reviews.  They also have a Plus version that supports Netflix and a "Hub" version that has a built in internal hard drive and a better GUI and shit.
